    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Race:</strong> Syrinx&nbsp;<br /><strong>Replaced Trait(s):</strong> Nocturnal, Pride&nbsp;</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Syrinxes often have a natural talent for sensing how to unsettle and oppress other creatures. As a swift action, a syrinx can attempt a Sense Motive check against a DC of 10 + a creature's Hit Dice + its Charisma modifier or a DC of 10 + the creature's Bluff modifier, whichever is higher. On a success, syrinx gains a +4 racial bonus on Intimidate checks against that target and a +1 racial bonus to the DC of any fear effects she uses against that target. This racial trait replaces nocturnal and pride.</p>",
